# Override the base URL used in copied play prompts and DESIGN.md quick-start instructions.
# Useful when testing plays locally — set this to a tunnel URL (ngrok, cloudflared, etc.)
# so agents can reach your local dev server from outside.
#
# Unset (default): falls back to window.location.origin at copy time.
# On Vercel: set to your canonical domain (e.g. https://sistema-bay-seven.vercel.app)
# to avoid preview-deployment URLs leaking into copied prompts.
#
# Requires a dev server restart after changing.

# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://your-tunnel-url.ngrok.io
